{"tid":2366557,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[香港人是狗] 美國UCLA大學生籃球員在華盜竊 VS 「12港人案」偷越邊境","createTime":"2021-01-14T15:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T15:23:55.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6457d406291f33fef0a5827394afd122e20a93d","tid":2366557,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國大學生籃球員在華盜竊 總統求情後獲釋返美<br />\n2017年11月16日</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/800/cpsprodpb/13098/production/_98767977_hi043021567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F13098%2Fproduction%2F_98767977_hi043021567.jpg&h=4431906c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三名美國運動員在中國實施店鋪盜竊被捕，在美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）介入求情之後獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普事後暗示三名球員應該向他表示感謝，三人隨即向剛剛完成亞洲訪問的總統致謝。<br />\n<br />\n在一個新聞發佈會上，加州大學洛杉磯分校（UCLA）的籃球員利安吉洛&middot;波爾（LiAngelo Ball）、柯迪&middot;萊利（Cody Riley）以及賈倫&middot;希爾（Jalen Hill）承認自己在杭州一個購物商場內偷東西。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42007068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-42007068&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVaNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=fb763e13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-42007068&h=fdcaf7ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-42007068</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>譚耀宗認為「12港人案」判刑可算是從輕發落</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201230-24_1k9nR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201230-24_1k9nR_1200x0.png&h=33b291e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗認為12名港人偷越邊境等罪的案件，被告分別判處7個月至3年不等的有期徒刑，可算是從輕發落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567826-20201230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567826-20201230.htm&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVaNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=f9964ee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567826-20201230.htm&h=5c03f7d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567826-20201230.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StsZg3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStsZg3t.jpg&h=b1c1e65c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a04390360b2425096b8e06d9655522391fe8629","tid":2366557,"uid":72034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"咁又點呀，三票民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}